{"tid":2340476,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國特色動物園】支那版steam「蒸氣平台」將推出 ，大劣網民大叫：你不要過來","createTime":"2020-12-25T13:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T15:16:13.000Z","uid":373533,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"87fdd8c9f61726c5372352d3b900323c8fc7747a","tid":2340476,"uid":373533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"支那一直將外國各種程式閹割，以供大劣市民使用，今次輪到Steam遭遇毒手，推出完美世界代理的「蒸氣平台」。<br />\n<br />\n完美電競嘉年華官方微博宣布「蒸氣平台」將於2021年1 月 16 與 17 日的「完美電競嘉年華」上開放玩家試玩體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McW4LfN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcW4LfN.jpg&h=577cc120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource 1:<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/games/steamcn-135724979.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fgames%2Fsteamcn-135724979.html&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQP%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=3ad513cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/games/steamcn-135724979.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4mkiu2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4mkiu2.png&h=8ff9abc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當遊戲在「蒸汽平台」發行時，廠商必須須遵守3個&ldquo;Steam中國政策&rdquo;選項：<br />\n<br />\n1.支持文本過濾（必須開啟）<br />\n<br />\n2.支持防沉迷系統（​​必須開啟）<br />\n<br />\n3.開啟遊玩遊戲前的健康提示<br />\n<br />\n這意味著支那玩家遊玩時有強制遊戲公告，遊玩不同遊戲有不同的遊戲時間限制，如某遊戲或會一天只可遊玩3小時。<br />\n<br />\n「蒸汽平台」和Steam亦是互相獨立的存在，兩者互不相干，減少了steam的支那用戶，遊戲不停出現外掛的問題或會得到改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource 2:<a href=\"https://www.league-funny.com/steam/article-146245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.league-funny.com%2Fsteam%2Farticle-146245&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQP%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=463eb553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.league-funny.com/steam/article-146245</a><br />\n<br />\n國際版 Steam 將成為大劣網民的烏托邦，然而翻牆跨區行為或將在steam受到限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前台灣獨立開發者 Leonard H. 製作的遊戲《赤毒》（Red Virus）被大陸小粉紅憤而在 Steam 以台獨、傷害「國家主席」形象為由舉報。<br />\n<br />\nSteam 客服將這位小粉紅的帳號「送中」，被客服從俄羅斯區丟回中國區ip ，實在是可喜可賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVZ6ea2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVZ6ea2.jpg&h=eb784b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由此可見，大劣網民翻牆steam跨區或成過去，跨區行為也有可能導致帳號封禁。<br />\n<br />\n大劣網民紛紛留言：「堅決堅持一個steam原則不動搖，蒸汽平台滾出中國」、「steam中國滾出中國」、「你不要過來」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPUmNy3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPUmNy3.jpg&h=0de6dfce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請社會主義接班人一定要拒絕資本主義電子鴉片！愛黨！愛習大大！粉紅再也不怕這些遊戲so辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c155a2c8f9c365eba74fab0b1a3e84d831b2d6","tid":2340476,"uid":284432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b3f0c02d447d3e2c2d71913d7a42afcdc2ae743","tid":2340476,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba315bc2342369f2d030ac1d08e412cf67887ac","tid":2340476,"uid":117276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94c155a2c8f9c365eba74fab0b1a3e84d831b2d6","tid":2340476,"uid":284432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會遲啲香港都強制轉支那steam<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e051bbe1f7ea16eba87e61af2999163303c1a151","tid":2340476,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b54b65eb43b67b0087a1ca5f245dcf55a7d4d558","tid":2340476,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba315bc2342369f